{"article_id":"ShnMegPaOLcI5AkU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi is facing mounting pressure over her future , with calls from members of her own party to step aside","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as discussions about potential successors gain more traction","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"-- both in the national spotlight and among members of Congress .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Pelosi has repeatedly said","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"she 's not going anywhere ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and she 's challenging anyone","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"who wants to run for speaker","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"-- should Democrats retake the House in November --","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to prove","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"they have what it takes","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"to lead the party .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"The future of Democratic leadership in the House is a topic","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"many in the party 's leadership are desperate to keep out of the headlines ahead of the midterms ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"hoping to keep the spotlight on an energized base rather than intraparty debates .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"While Democrats feel optimistic about their chances","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"at retaking the House ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"who will lead the party is another question all together .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"With so many variables at stake","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"-- mostly whether Pelosi can get the 218 votes","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"needed to become speaker --","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"and no clear next-in-line candidate ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"some members are positioning themselves ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"preparing for a possible vacancy at the top of the party .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Those conversations are largely taking place behind the scenes at this point","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"-- though some of have spilled over into public view this week --","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"but all under the context as possible backup scenarios","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"if Pelosi does n't run .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` Where two or more members are gathered in Washington ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"invariably the discussion about House leadership comes up , ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"Democratic Rep. Brian Higgins of New York ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"who has already stated","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"he wo n't support Pelosi this fall ,","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"told CNN in a phone interview Thursday .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"One of Pelosi 's closest allies , however , is publicly expressing interest in the speaker 's gavel .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Rep. James Clyburn of South Carolina , the No . 3 Democrat in the House , says","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"he 'll support Pelosi","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"if she decides to stay","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"--","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"but he 's also ready to step in","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"if she does n't .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"For her part , Pelosi is counting on her experience as well as her colossal fundraising power","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to shore up her path","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"to return to the speakership .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Pelosi was also lauded by her party","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"for helping to usher through the Affordable Care Act","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"when Democrats controlled the House during the first two years under President Barack Obama .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Since Republicans have taken back the majority ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"she has largely kept her caucus together","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"in opposing big Republican initiatives","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and has had no major defections on key votes .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Even those","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"who want to see new leadership","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"still routinely praise her 15-year tenure as leader of the caucus .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"As Pelosi put it to MSNBC last weekend ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"I 'm the best person for the job . ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Clyburn ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"if elected speaker ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"would be the first black Democratic Speaker of the US House of Representatives .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"`` If the opportunity is there","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"I would absolutely do it , ''","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Clyburn told The New York Times ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"citing a verse from scripture on the importance","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"of `` keeping your lamps trimmed and burning","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to be ready","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"when the bridegroom comes . ''","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Clyburn also told Politico earlier this month ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"`` If the opportunity is there ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"absolutely .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"I have been preparing myself for this role since my pre-teenage years . ''","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"A host of other names are frequently mentioned by lawmakers and aides as potential Pelosi-alternatives ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"including other members of the Congressional Black Caucus , such as the chairman , Rep. Cedric Richmond of Louisiana , and Rep. Hakeem Jeffries of New York .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Rep. Cheri Bustos of Illinois and Rep. Ben Ray Luján of New Mexico are two other names , among many more ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"who get dropped as potential candidates","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"seeking higher leadership positions .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"House Minority Whip Steny Hoyer , the current No . 2 Democrat in the House , is also considered a likely contender for the top spot","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"should Pelosi step aside .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"He and Clyburn vied for the whip position in 2010 ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"but","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"after it was clear Clyburn would not get enough support ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"he was offered the newly-created position of Assistant Democratic Leader ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"averting a divisive caucus vote between Clyburn and Hoyer .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Rep. Tim Ryan of Ohio ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"who challenged Pelosi in the last leadership race in 2016 ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"has said","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"he 's considering launching another challenge","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"if Pelosi stays .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"But there 's no consensus around any successor ,","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"as most are keeping their powder dry until the month after the midterms","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"when it 's clear what Pelosi will do","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"and when other leadership campaigns launch into full swing .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"The caucus elections ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"which take place on a secret ballot ,","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"are slated for the week of December 5 .","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"`` I look forward to seeing the results of the election","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"and assessing","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"who opts to run for leadership after the outcome , ''","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"said Rep. Dan Lipinski of Illinois ,","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"who voted against Pelosi in 2016 .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"Pelosi has faced dissension in the Democratic Party this cycle ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"as a growing number of candidates and some incumbents have expressed ambivalence towards her potential bid for speaker ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"including rising Democratic star Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"who told CNN","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"it was `` far too early ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to back a candidate for speaker","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"following her surprise primary win in June ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"and Massachusetts Rep. Seth Moulton ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"who called for `` a new generation of leadership , '' in a July interview with CNN .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Supporters of Pelosi say","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"she 's getting unfair treatment","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"that 's largely based on her age rather than her abilities and leadership of the party .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"While at least 37 new Democratic candidates and incumbents ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"according to a CNN count ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"have said","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"they wo n't support Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"many others are showing deference to whatever decision she ultimately makes .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Before the Times published its interview with Clyburn this week ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Rep. Elijah Cummings of Maryland was asked Sunday on ABC 's `` This Week ''","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"if he felt","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"it was time for an African American speaker .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"it was `` quite possible . '","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"' `` But I 'd bet everything","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"I 've got","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"that Nancy Pelosi will be Speaker , period , ''","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"In an interview with McClatchy , the 78-year-old Clyburn pledged","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"a Clyburn speakership would be `` transitional , '' not `` custodial , ''","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"and that he 'd seek to make the Democratic Party more attractive `` to young African Americans","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"who still feel ... take ( n ) for granted . '' `` I think","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"our party needs to be transformed","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"and that 's what I 'm talking about , ''","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Clyburn said .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"But Pelosi seemed unruffled at the prospect of others","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"showing interest in the speakership ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"telling the Times ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"`` What I have always tried to do is build a bridge to the future ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"and hope","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"that would be in the majority .","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"If people want to be the bridge","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"that I 'm building toward ,","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"they have to show what 's on the other side of the bridge . ''","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Pelosi 's confidence is well-founded - internal documents","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"obtained by CNN from the Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"show","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that the House minority leader raised an impressive $ 83 million through June for the 2018 election cycle ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"more than doubling the party 's next highest fundraiser , DCCC chair Rep. Ben Ray Lujan ,","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"who raised $ 35 million .","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"Clyburn , for his part , has raised $ 3.7 million for the party 's House campaign arm .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"In The New York Times interview , Pelosi challenged anyone","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"who wants to run for speaker","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"to prove","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"they have the fundraising prowess","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"it takes","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"to lead the party ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"as well as demonstrate","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"they have `` a following '' and `` a vision for the country . ''","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"Despite aggressive messaging by Republicans","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"to paint Pelosi as a villain ,","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"the idea of another Pelosi speakership does n't seem to sway voters one way or the other -","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"in a CNN poll out this week , just 34 % of registered voters said","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Pelosi will be an extremely or very important factor in their vote in 2018 ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"putting her at the bottom of their voting considerations .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"While leadership race chatter will undoubtedly ramp up again","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"when members return next month from recess ,","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"Democrats","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"-- both Pelosi detractors and supporters --","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"are still largely trying to stay on message for now .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"Rep. Ruben Gallego of Arizona ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"who voted against Pelosi during the leadership race in 2016 ,","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"reiterated over the weekend on MSNBC the common refrain","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"that Democrats should solely focus on winning back the majority .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"`` Because until then , this is all a moot point , ''","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"he said .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":351,"left":0,"right":350,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":350,"left":266,"right":349,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":186,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":178,"right":185,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":178,"left":1,"right":177,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":179,"right":184,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":4,"rig